<section class="ezy-calculator-section" id="quote-calculator">
    <div class="calc-container">
        <div class="calc-card">
            <div class="calc-header-row">
                <div class="stepper-dots">
                    <div class="dot active"></div>
                    <div class="dot"></div>
                    <div class="dot"></div>
                    <div class="dot"></div>
                    <div class="dot"></div>
                    <div class="dot"></div>
                    <div class="dot"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="price-display">
                    <span class="price-label">ESTIMATED BUDGET</span>
                    <strong id="totalPrice">₹ 0</strong>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="calc-body-area">
                <div id="stepContent"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="calc-footer-actions">
                <button id="prevBtn" class="btn-back" onclick="changeStep(-1)">
                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
                </button>
                <button id="nextBtn" class="btn-continue" onclick="changeStep(1)">
                    <span id="btnText">Continue</span> 
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-right" id="btnIcon"></i>
                    <div class="loader-spinner" id="btnLoader" style="display:none;"></div>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="successPopup" class="ezy-modal-overlay" style="display:none;">
        <div class="ezy-modal-card">
            <div class="success-icon" style="font-size: 50px; color: #10b981; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
            </div>
            <h2 style="font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #1e293b;">Quote Request Sent!</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: #64748b;">Our Jaipur experts will contact you within 24 hours to discuss your project.</p>
            <button class="btn-continue" style="width:100%;" onclick="location.reload()">Back to Home</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    /* 1. CONTAINER & SCOPE */
    .ezy-calculator-section {
        background: #f8fafc; /* Subtle light background to distinguish from hero */
        padding: 60px 20px;
        scroll-margin-top: 100px;
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif !important;
        display: block;
    }

    .calc-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        position: relative;
    }

    /* 2. COMPACT CALCULATOR CARD */
    .calc-card {
        max-width: 520px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 30px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }

    .calc-header-row { 
        display: flex; 
        justify-content: space-between; 
        align-items: center; 
        margin-bottom: 25px; 
    }

    /* Stepper Dots */
    .stepper-dots { display: flex; gap: 6px; }
    .dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; background: #e2e8f0; border-radius: 50%; transition: 0.3s; }
    .dot.active { background: #4f46e5; width: 24px; border-radius: 10px; }

    /* Price Label */
    .price-display { text-align: right; }
    .price-label { display: block; font-size: 10px; color: #64748b; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; }
    .price-display strong { font-size: 24px; color: #0f172a; font-weight: 800; }

    /* Content Area */
    .calc-body-area { min-height: 280px; } 

    /* Typography inside JS content */
    .step-ui h2 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .step-ui p { font-size: 14px; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 20px; }

    /* List Options Styling */
    .list-options { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
    .opt-item { 
        display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 14px 18px; border: 2px solid #f1f5f9; 
        border-radius: 16px; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.2s; gap: 12px; 
    }
    .opt-item:hover { background: #f8fafc; border-color: #e2e8f0; }
    .opt-item.selected { border-color: #4f46e5; background: #f5f3ff; }
    .opt-item i { font-size: 18px; color: #4f46e5; width: 25px; text-align: center; }
    .opt-info b { font-size: 15px; color: #0f172a; display: block; }
    .opt-info span { font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; }

    .calc-input { 
        width: 100%; padding: 14px; border: 2px solid #e2e8f0; 
        border-radius: 12px; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; 
        font-family: inherit;
    }

    /* 3. BUTTONS */
    .calc-footer-actions { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-top: 30px; gap: 12px; }
    
    .btn-continue { 
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #7c3aed 100%); 
        color: white; border: none; 
        padding: 16px; border-radius: 16px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; 
        cursor: pointer; flex: 3; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 10px;
        transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-continue:active { transform: scale(0.98); }

    .btn-back { 
        background: #f1f5f9; border: none; color: #64748b; 
        padding: 16px; border-radius: 16px; flex: 1; cursor: pointer; 
        transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-back:hover { background: #e2e8f0; }

    /* 4. SUCCESS POPUP */
    .ezy-modal-overlay { 
        position: fixed; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; 
        background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.85); z-index: 9999; 
        display: none; align-items: center; justify-content: center; 
        padding: 20px; backdrop-filter: blur(4px); 
    }
    .ezy-modal-card { 
        background: #fff; padding: 40px 30px; border-radius: 24px; 
        text-align: center; max-width: 400px; width: 100%;
        box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .ezy-calculator-section { padding: 40px 15px; }
        .calc-card { padding: 20px; }
        .calc-body-area { min-height: 300px; }
    }
</style>


<section class="seo-keywords">
<div class="s-container">

<h2>Average Website Development Cost for Different Businesses</h2>

<p>
The cost of a website varies depending on business type. A restaurant or cloud kitchen website may cost less than an ecommerce marketplace or learning management system.
Small business websites in India generally cost between ₹15,000 and ₹30,000 while ecommerce platforms can range from ₹45,000 to ₹80,000 depending on integrations and custom design.
</p>

</div>
</section>

