<section class="seo-explainer-v1">
  <div class="s-container">

    <div class="s-header">
      <span class="s-badge">Market Insight</span>
      <h2>Website Cost Calculator for Indian Businesses</h2>
      <p>Instantly estimate your website development cost based on real business needs — driven by data, not guesswork.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="s-grid">
      <div class="s-card">
        <div class="s-icon">⚙️</div>
        <h3>How This Works</h3>
        <p>Answer a few questions about your pages, SEO, and design needs. Our engine calculates a realistic budget range instantly based on current Indian market rates.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s-card">
        <div class="s-icon">💰</div>
        <h3>Pricing Factors</h3>
        <ul class="s-list">
          <li><span>•</span> Website type (Business, E-com, LMS)</li>
          <li><span>•</span> Number of custom pages & content</li>
          <li><span>•</span> Advanced SEO & Analytics setup</li>
          <li><span>•</span> Custom UI/UX & Branding depth</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="s-card highlight">
        <div class="s-icon">🇮🇳</div>
        <h3>Cost in India</h3>
        <p>In India, professional websites typically range from <strong>₹15,000 to ₹50,000+</strong>. This tool provides a benchmark to help you plan your digital investment.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="s-header breakdown-head">
      <h2>Website Development Cost in India</h2>
      <p>A detailed breakdown of common pricing tiers for Indian startups and established brands.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="s-grid">
      <div class="s-card tier-card">
        <div class="s-icon">🏢</div>
        <h4>Standard Business</h4>
        <div class="s-price-range">₹15,000 - ₹25,000</div>
        <p>Best for local businesses needing a professional 5-10 page site with contact forms and basic SEO.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s-card tier-card">
        <div class="s-icon">🛒</div>
        <h4>Ecommerce Store</h4>
        <div class="s-price-range">₹45,000 - ₹80,000+</div>
        <p>Includes payment gateway, inventory management, and product catalogs for D2C brands.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s-card tier-card">
        <div class="s-icon">🎨</div>
        <h4>Custom UI/UX</h4>
        <div class="s-price-range">Variable Pricing</div>
        <p>Focused on unique branding and high-conversion layouts tailored specifically for your target audience.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="s-footer-note">
      <p>Serving businesses in <strong>Jaipur, Delhi, Mumbai, Bangalore</strong> and across India. Free technical audit included with every quote.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
    /* 1. SECTION CONTAINER & FONT ALIGNMENT */
    .seo-explainer-v1 {
        padding: 80px 0;
        background: var(--bg-light);
        /* Matches EzyGoDigi Poppins Branding */
